================================================================================
Models
================================================================================

Depth Anything V2 (Small) — relative depth estimation
    ONNX weights: onnx-community/depth-anything-v2-small (Hugging Face)
    License: Apache-2.0
    Downloaded at install/first-run into models/ (not redistributed here).

RTMPose / RTMDet, via rtmlib — body detection + pose estimation
    https://github.com/Tau-J/rtmlib  (models from the MMPose project)
    License: Apache-2.0
    Pose weights are fetched into the rtmlib cache on first use.

TopFormer (ADE20K, 512) — sky/ground backdrop for the layout blockout
    Architecture: TopFormer (https://github.com/hustvl/TopFormer), trained on
    ADE20K (MIT Scene Parsing Benchmark). ONNX weights self-hosted on the
    project's GitHub releases (models-v1).
    License: Apache-2.0
    Downloaded at install/first-run into models/ (not redistributed here).

YOLOX (tiny / l) — foreground object detection for the layout blockout
    https://github.com/Megvii-BaseDetection/YOLOX  (trained on COCO)
    License: Apache-2.0
    Pre-exported ONNX fetched from YOLOX's own release (tag 0.1.1rc0) at
    install/first-run into models/ (not redistributed here).

