================================================================================
Demo footage
================================================================================

The bundled demo projects (backend/app/assets/demos/) ship only DERIVED control
signals — extracted frames, pose, depth and layout sequences plus thumbnails.
The original source videos are NOT redistributed with this project.

Those signals were derived from short, publicly available sample clips:
    - Pexels (pexels.com) — free-to-use stock footage (street / crossing scenes)
    - OpenCV / Intel sample media — bundled test clips (courtyard / corridor scenes)

Demo content is provided solely to illustrate the pipeline and can be deleted at
any time (it is only recreated on an explicit reset or a first launch).
